# Tupload - Golang Multipart/Base64 File Upload Library

## Install
``` bash
$ go get github.com/tusupov/tupload
```

## Example

#### from Multipart Form
``` go

file := r.MultipartForm.File["image"][0]

fileName, err := tupload.ImageMultipart(*file, "/var/www/images");
if err != nil {
	//Upload end with error
}

```

#### from Url
``` go

url := "https://golang.org/doc/gopher/project.png"

fileName, err := tupload.ImageUrl(url, "/var/www/images");
if err != nil {
	//Upload end with error
}

```

#### from Base64
``` go

b64 := "data:image/png;base64,"

fileName, err := tupload.ImageBase64(b64, "/var/www/images");
if err != nil {
	//Upload end with error
}

```
